title: Richard Nixon - In the Arena (A Memoir) 1990
description:
Richard Nixon
IN THE ARENA: A MEMOIR OF VICTORY, DEFEAT AND RENEWAL
(Simon and Schuster Audio, 1990)

Written and read by Richard Nixon

His 3rd and final memoir . . .

Original, official abridged audiobook. Nobody reads Nixon like Nixon does.

Digital transfer from audio cassettes.
MP3 encoded @ 256 kbps

Divided into chapters according to the book layout. Some chapters are longer than others; thus, some files are larger than others.

Nearly exactly 3 hours long.
